name: 格雷西·罗宾斯
name_full: 格雷西·罗宾斯 Gracie Robbin
introduction: Gracie Robbin is a film and theatre actress born and raised in Toronto, Ontario. Gracie holds a Bachelor of Fine Arts from the University of Windsor's Acting Conservatory Program. She has trained internationally, also holding a training certificate from the Moscow Art Theatre School's "Month in Moscow" program. Gracie has performed on stages across Canada, and lives in Toronto advancing her film and television career.
